sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detector as Detector Service<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>{"stream": false, "messages": [...]}
        Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector definitions<br/>Set stream=false
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: Bearer token (forwarded)<br/>x-forwarded-* headers<br/>Optional mTLS client cert<br/>{"detectors": {...}, "messages": [...]}
        Orchestrator->>Detector: Content detection request<br/>(input detectors)
        Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>vLLM: Chat completion request<br/>{"messages": [...]}
        vLLM-->>Orchestrator: LLM response
        Orchestrator->>Detector: Content detection request<br/>(output detectors)
        Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with detections
        alt Detections found & fallback_message configured
            Note over Gateway: Replace response choices<br/>with fallback_message
            Gateway-->>Client: Modified JSON response<br/>(fallback message)
        else No detections or no fallback
            Gateway-->>Client: Original JSON response
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>{"stream": true, "messages": [...]}
        Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector definitions<br/>Set stream=true
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: Bearer token (forwarded)<br/>Optional mTLS client cert<br/>{"stream": true, "detectors": {...}}
        loop SSE byte stream
            Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: {"choices": [...], "detections": [...]}\n\n
            alt Detection in chunk & fallback_message configured
                Note over Gateway: Apply fallback_message<br/>to first chunk
                Gateway-->>Client: data: {"choices": [{"delta": {"content": "fallback"}}]}\n\n
            else No detection in chunk
                Gateway-->>Client: data: {"choices": [{"delta": {"content": "..."}}]}\n\n
            end
        end
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: [DONE]\n\n
        Gateway-->>Client: data: [DONE]\n\n
    end
